Package change

Class Summary
Change Change entity represents filesystem and group changes (updates).
ChangeFactory A Factory-type component for creating Change objects, either filesystem or group changes.
ChangeLogger Repository for Change objects.
ChangeQueryCriteria Value object representing the properties of a ChangeLog query.
ChangeService Interface for the change module, offering the means for the other components to store and access changes.
